                    <span>Spencer Johnson has addressed so much more than change in this remarkable little book.  I have found in Who Moved My Cheese? principles of goal setting, positive mental attitude, entrepreneurialism, courage, persistence, being action-oriented, not getting caught in over analysis.  A real practical storybook for young people to learn what it takes to have a fulfilling career and life.  A Brilliant and Simple book.</span>
                  
